DESCRIPTION:<p>Every Wednesday morning\, April–October 2026<br></p><p>If yo
 u live near these greenways and work at or near NC State or Downtown Raleig
 h\, or anywhere along the route\, this is for you. Or do you work from home
  and just want a friendly\, casual morning ride? Join us!</p><p>You do not 
 have to start at Lockwood Park. Hop on anywhere along the route and leave w
 henever you need. Ride the whole way or just a segment that fits your commu
 te.</p><p>The pace is casual\, around 12 mph. This is technically a “drop r
 ide” so we can stay on schedule and arrive in Downtown Raleigh by 9:00 AM.<
 /p><p>GREEN LINE SCHEDULE:<br>7:30 AM: Lockwood Park – Departure<br>7:45 AM
 : Industrial Dr – Ride by<br>7:48 AM: Kiwanis Park – Ride by<br>7:50 AM: An
