 operative project located in Raleigh\, NC and established in 2017. We are c
 urrently partnering with homeless resource centers in the Raleigh area to r
 epair bicycles and teach maintenance skills. Want to get involved? We'll te
 ach you basic repair skills so you can give back to our community!<br><br><
 b>Registration required</b>: No\, but if you'd like to volunteer to help fi
 x bikes\, reach out to volunteer@raleighcommunitykickstand.org.<br><b>Passp
 ort eligible?</b> Yes\, if you volunteer!<br><b>Community partner</b>: Rale
 igh Community Kickstand
